What you've done.

1977
02:18:06.250 --> 02:18:08.125
That's a lot more important than revenge.

1978
02:18:09.875 --> 02:18:11.541
I used to only believe in myself.

1979
02:18:12.625 --> 02:18:14.416
In myself and my tech.

1980
02:18:15.875 --> 02:18:18.458
